title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
OB: When previewing the report and clicking on the 'Show Report Parameters' button, the default values are not displayed in the value box.
EB: The expected behavior is that the default values should be shown in the value box, allowing me to modify the parameters that I want to change.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Preview the report. 2. Click on the 'Show Report Parameters' button.
